---
import { getWhatsAppUrl, getPlanWhatsAppUrl } from '../../utils/whatsapp';

const primaryCta = getPlanWhatsAppUrl('crecimiento');
const secondaryCta = getWhatsAppUrl("Hola, me gustaría ver una demo de cómo funciona el chatbot con IA para mi negocio.");
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="badge">IA + AUTOMATIZACIÓN DE VENTAS</div>
      <h1 class="headline">
        Haz que tu negocio <br/>
        <span>responda, venda y crezca</span> <br/>
        en automático
      </h1>
      <p class="subcopy">
        La herramienta definitiva para automatizar tus canales de ventas, calificar prospectos y agendar citas 24/7 sin contratar más personal.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href={primaryCta} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary" data-ga-event="cta_click">
          Comenzar Gratis
        </a>
        <a href={secondaryCta} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-secondary" data-ga-event="cta_click">
          Ver Demo en Vivo
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-trust">
        <div class="trust-avatars">
          <div class="avatar">👨‍💻</div>
          <div class="avatar">👩‍💼</div>
          <div class="avatar">👨‍💼</div>
        </div>
        <p>Más de 50 negocios en Cancún ya automatizan sus ventas.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="phone-mockup">
        <div class="phone-header">
          <div class="phone-user">
            <span class="user-status"></span>
            <div>
              <p class="user-name">Asistente Inteligente</p>
              <p class="user-info">En línea</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="phone-chat">
          <div class="chat-bubble user">
            Hola! Me interesa información de los servicios.
          </div>
          <div class="chat-bubble bot">
            ¡Hola! Con gusto. ¿Qué tipo de negocio tienes actualmente? 
            <span class="options">1. Servicios Locales<br/>2. Inmobiliaria / Real Estate<br/>3. E-commerce</span>
          </div>
          <div class="chat-bubble user delay-1">
            2. Inmobiliaria
          </div>
          <div class="chat-bubble bot delay-2">
            ¡Excelente! 🏢 Con el plan <strong>Crecimiento Automático</strong> calificamos tus leads y agendamos directo en tu calendario. ¿Te gustaría agendar una demo en vivo?
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="glow-bg"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .badge {
    background: rgba(163, 113, 247, 0.1);
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border: 1px solid rgba(163, 113, 247, 0.2);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .headline {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .headline span {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-primary) 0%, var(--accent-secondary) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .subcopy {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 540px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: transform var(--transition-fast), box-shadow var(--transition-fast), background var(--transition-fast);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-primary) 0%, rgba(163, 113, 247, 0.8) 100%);
    color: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(163, 113, 247, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(163, 113, 247, 0.5);
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    color: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .hero-trust {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .trust-avatars {
    display: flex;
  }

  .avatar {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 2px solid var(--bg-primary);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-left: -8px;
  }

  .avatar:first-child {
    margin-left: 0;
  }

  .hero-trust p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Phone Mockup visual */
  .hero-visual {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .phone-mockup {
    width: 300px;
    height: 520px;
    background: #0f0f15;
    border: 8px solid #20202b;
    border-radius: 36px;
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), 0 0 40px rgba(163, 113, 247, 0.15);
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .phone-header {
    background: #161622;
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem 0.8rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .phone-user {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .user-status {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--accent-secondary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--accent-secondary);
  }

  .user-name {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .user-info {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .phone-chat {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    overflow-y: auto;
    background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 1px, transparent 0);
    background-size: 16px 16px;
  }

  .chat-bubble {
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 18px;
    font-size: 0.825rem;
    max-width: 80%;
    line-height: 1.4;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) both;
  }

  .chat-bubble.user {
    background: #1f1f2e;
    color: #e8e8ed;
    align-self: flex-end;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
  }

  .chat-bubble.bot {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(163, 113, 247, 0.15) 0%, rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.05) 100%);
    color: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(163, 113, 247, 0.15);
    align-self: flex-start;
    border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
  }

  .chat-bubble .options {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    padding-top: 0.5rem;
    border-top: 1px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .delay-1 {
    animation-delay: 1.5s;
  }

  .delay-2 {
    animation-delay: 3s;
  }

  .glow-bg {
    position: absolute;
    width: 350px;
    height: 350px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(163, 113, 247, 0.15) 0%, rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.05) 70%, transparent 100%);
    z-index: 1;
    filter: blur(40px);
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(10px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .hero-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .hero-content {
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .subcopy {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .hero-buttons {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-trust {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .headline {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .phone-mockup {
      width: 100%;
      height: 480px;
    }
  }
</style>
